General Automation Inc said itsigned a joint venture with Madrid, Spain-based Ingenieria DeSistemas Electronics S.A.    The pact establishes General Automation Iberica S.A. as alocal manufacturer and master distributor of GeneralAutomation's ZEBRA multi-user business systems in Spain andPortugal.    General Automation Iberica will be equally financed byGeneral Automation and Ingenieria. Reuter&#3;